data.name: ImageStatus
desc: These values are used to specify to which degree an image is available.

items.name: IMAGESTATUS_ERROR
lines: This conveys that an error was encountered while producing the image.

items.name: IMAGESTATUS_SINGLEFRAMEDONE
lines: This conveys that one frame of the image is complete but there are more frames to be delivered.

items.name: IMAGESTATUS_STATICIMAGEDONE
lines: This conveys that the image is complete and there are no more pixels or frames to be delivered.

items.name: IMAGESTATUS_ABORTED
lines: This conveys that the image creation process was deliberately aborted.
